    <item>
      <title>波音评论家称他与联邦调查局分享了失踪的 737 Bolt 记录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/boeing-critic-says-he-shared-missing-737-bolt-records-with-fbi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波音公司的一位著名批评者反驳了该飞机制造商的说法，即没有记录表明机身面板后来在飞行中从 737 Max 9 上爆炸，引发了该公司的质量信任危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/boeing-critic-says-he-shared-missing-737-bolt-records-with-fbi</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 18:13:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟领导人敦促“范式转变”以扭转欧洲衰落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/eu-leaders-to-urge-paradigm-shift-to-reverse-european-decline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟相对于主要地缘政治对手的影响力不断减弱，给欧洲各国首都敲响了警钟，迫使各国领导人讨论彻底转型，以提高欧盟在充满敌意的世界中的竞争力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/eu-leaders-to-urge-paradigm-shift-to-reverse-european-decline</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 18:10:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果共和党推翻约翰逊，这些人可能是众议院议长的竞争者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/familiar-names-wild-cards-among-contenders-if-gop-ousts-johnson</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党上一次罢免自己的众议院议长时，花了三周时间和几次内爆，才最终选定相对不知名的迈克·约翰逊（路易斯安那州共和党人）作为替代者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/familiar-names-wild-cards-among-contenders-if-gop-ousts-johnson</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 18:07:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普推动全民征收 17% 所得税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/kudlow-forbes-push-trump-to-embrace-17-flat-tax-fewer-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普受到其圈子里的经济学家的压力，要求其采取统一税率、更温和的贸易立场并控制州和地方的税收减免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/kudlow-forbes-push-trump-to-embrace-17-flat-tax-fewer-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 18:01:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国核导弹潜艇因弓、发电机问题推迟了长达 16 个月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/nuclear-missile-sub-delayed-up-to-16-months-over-bow-generators</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国第一艘哥伦比亚级核导弹潜艇的交付延迟了长达 16 个月——海军的首要武器——根据该部门的内部评估，这是由于承包商延迟交付船首部分和发电机所致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/nuclear-missile-sub-delayed-up-to-16-months-over-bow-generators</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 18:01:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西央行警告投资者不确定性不断增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/brazil-s-central-bank-warns-investors-of-growing-uncertainties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西央行行长罗伯托·坎波斯·内托(Roberto Campos Neto)告诉投资者，自上次货币政策会议以来，不确定性有所增加，因为经济学家正在权衡政策制定者放慢降息的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/brazil-s-central-bank-warns-investors-of-growing-uncertainties</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 17:51:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 剥离或禁止法案即将在美国国会快速通过</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/tiktok-divest-or-ban-bill-moving-on-fast-track-through-congress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据众议院议长迈克·约翰逊周三概述的一项计划，迫使 TikTok 的中国母公司字节跳动有限公司剥离其社交媒体平台所有权的努力将很快成为法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/tiktok-divest-or-ban-bill-moving-on-fast-track-through-congress</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 17:26:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>约翰逊议长无视强硬派，推进乌克兰和以色列计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/speaker-johnson-defies-hardliners-presses-ahead-on-ukraine-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[面对共和党强硬派驱逐他的威胁，美国众议院议长迈克·约翰逊正在继续向乌克兰和以色列提供新的援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/speaker-johnson-defies-hardliners-presses-ahead-on-ukraine-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 15:39:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波音公司重置安全文化还有“很长的路要走”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/boeing-has-long-way-to-go-to-fix-safety-culture-after-accident</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国立法者要求波音公司花费必要的时间和精力来重塑他们所谓的破损的安全文化，并批评该飞机制造商与监管机构的关系过于融洽。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/boeing-has-long-way-to-go-to-fix-safety-culture-after-accident</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 14:55:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍勃·梅南德斯准备在贿赂案辩护中指责他的妻子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/bob-menendez-poised-to-blame-his-wife-in-bribery-case-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份新公布的法庭文件显示，美国参议员鲍勃·梅嫩德斯准备在受贿案审判中指责他的妻子向他隐瞒了有关他们据称从寻求好处的商人那里收受礼物的信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/bob-menendez-poised-to-blame-his-wife-in-bribery-case-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 23:42:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
